[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> # For a reverse primer to create overhang ATGA on the fragment:
[?2004l[?2004h> # The reverse primer on the bottom strand needs to have the RC of ATGA
[?2004l[?2004h> # 5' ...GAGACC N TCAT [template RC] 3'
[?2004l[?2004h> # After cutting, the fragment will have ...ATGA-5' on the other end
[?2004l[?2004h> 
